      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 20.施密特正交化</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="施密特正交化">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%96%bd%e5%af%86%e7%89%b9%e6%ad%a3%e4%ba%a4%e5%8c%96"></a>
施密特正交化
</h2><p>设向量组 $\alpha_1,\alpha_2,\alpha_3,\dots,\alpha_s$ 线性无关，令
</p>
$$
\begin{cases} 
\beta_1 = \alpha_1 \\[4pt] \beta_2 = \alpha_2 - \dfrac{[\alpha_2,\beta_1]}{[\beta_1,\beta_1]}\beta_1 \\[4pt] \beta_3 = \alpha_3 - \dfrac{[\alpha_3,\beta_1]}{[\beta_1,\beta_1]}\beta_1 - \dfrac{[\alpha_3,\beta_2]}{[\beta_2,\beta_2]}\beta_2 
\\...
\end{cases}
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/20.%E6%96%BD%E5%AF%86%E7%89%B9%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E5%8C%96/image-20260711104932615.png" alt="image-20260711104932615"></p>
